	(text "Design notes: Use one 0-ohm series jumper footprint on every PZT+ line, optional 1M-10M bleed resistor across each PZT, 100nF decoupling at every CD74HC4067 VCC pin, 1uF bulk cap near J1, guarded analog routing, and test pads for JACK_SIG, VCC, GND, MUX_S0-S3, BANK0-BANK2, and each mux COM." (at 20.00 335.00 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left bottom)))
